If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : podpora@immaxneo.cz

Immax NEO PRO products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 

After connecting Alexa to your Immax NEO products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Immax NEO PRO" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Immax NEO account in our "Immax NEO PRO" app;
(3). You need to have some Immax NEO devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Immax NEO PRO app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Immax NEO PRO" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Immax NEO PRO" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Immax NEO PRO", and you'll be navigated to Immax NEO PRO login page;
(9). Input your Immax NEO PRO account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
